+    Idle --> CreateFile: Click "New File" hover btn<br/>or context menu "New File"
+    Idle --> CreateFolder: Click "New Folder" hover btn<br/>or context menu "New Folder"
+    Idle --> Rename: F2 / Enter / context menu "Rename"
